    "Most domestic charging stations in Switzerland, Germany, Austria and Denmark are 3-phase. Change only if you know yours is 1-phase." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the 3-phase charging stations in the EU.",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De fleste hjemme-ladestationer i Schweiz, Tyskland, Østrig og Danmark er 3-fasede. Ændr kun, hvis du ved, at din er 1-faset."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die meisten Heim-Ladestationen in der Schweiz, Deutschland, Österreich und Dänemark sind 3-phasig. Ändere das nur, wenn deine 1-phasig ist."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La plupart des bornes domestiques en Suisse, en Allemagne, en Autriche et au Danemark sont triphasées. Ne changez que si vous savez que la vôtre est monophasée."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La maggior parte delle stazione di ricarica domestiche in Svizzera, Germania, Austria e Danimarca è trifase. Cambia solo se sai che la tua è monofase."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Most domestic charging stations in Switzerland, Germany, Austria and Denmark are 3-phase. Pick \"Auto\" if your charging station switches between 1- and 3-phase based on load (e.g. go-eCharger, Easee)." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the available charging station phases.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De fleste hjemme-ladestationer i Schweiz, Tyskland, Østrig og Danmark er 3-fasede. Vælg „Auto“, hvis din ladestation skifter mellem 1- og 3-faset baseret på belastning (f.eks. go-eCharger, Easee)."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die meisten Heim-Ladestationen in der Schweiz, Deutschland, Österreich und Dänemark sind 3-phasig. Wähle „Auto“, wenn deine Ladestation abhängig von der Last zwischen 1- und 3-phasig wechselt (z. B. go-eCharger, Easee)."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Most domestic charging stations in Switzerland, Germany, Austria and Denmark are 3-phase. Pick \"Auto\" if your charging station switches between 1- and 3-phase based on load (e.g. go-eCharger, Easee)."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La plupart des bornes domestiques en Suisse, en Allemagne, en Autriche et au Danemark sont triphasées. Choisissez « Auto » si votre borne bascule entre monophasé et triphasé selon la charge (par ex. go-eCharger, Easee)."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La maggior parte delle stazione di ricarica domestiche in Svizzera, Germania, Austria e Danimarca è trifase. Seleziona “Auto” se la tua stazione di ricarica commuta tra mono- e trifase in base al carico (es. go-eCharger, Easee)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
